opensuse:
- PermitRootLogin yes (in /etc/ssh/sshd_config)
- dpkg alternative
- service reparse

centos:
- PasswordAuthentication yes, PermitRootLogin yes (in /etc/ssh/sshd_config)

alpine:
- PermitRootLogin yes (in /etc/ssh/sshd_config)
- install python (apk add python3)
- install lsof (not busybox version) (apk add lsof)